    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Erythraeus (Zaracarus) budapestensis Fain and Ripka, 1998, female: a—palp, medial aspect, b—non-sensillary seta (AM = AL), c—crista metopica, d—dorsal opisthosomal setae, e—ventral seta, f—genital opening, g—anal opening." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6622949/files/figure.png" ;
