<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6622955>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Erythraeus (Zaracarus) budapestensis Fain and Ripka, 1998, female: a—leg setae, deutonymph: b—palp, medial aspect, c—crista metopica, d—genital opening, e—anal opening." ;
