<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6622967>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Erythraeus (Zaracarus) budapestensis Fain and Ripka, 1998, larva: a—gnathosoma, ventral view, b—idiosoma, dorsal view, c—idiosoma, ventral view.Abbreviations: as—adoral seta, bs—hypostomal seta, cs—oral spine like seta, elcp—supracoxala, elcI—supracoxal seta on coxae I, ω—solenidion, ζ—eupathidium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6622967/files/figure.png" ;
