<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6622983>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Attachment sites of larval Erythraeus (Zaracarus) budapestensis Fain and Ripka, 1998, at Uroleucon spp. a—attached to the head and thorax, b—attached to the abdomen, c—attached to the antenna, d—attached to the leg. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6622983/files/figure.png" ;
